				<a class="comment-link" href="#37465">16 октября 2018 14:57</a>
			</div>

		<div class="l-text b-typo">
			<p>Lohika is&nbsp;one of&nbsp;the best companies in&nbsp;Lviv. Provides very good and comfortable work places with interesting projects and management. That was very good time to&nbsp;be&nbsp;a&nbsp;part of&nbsp;this company! During that period&nbsp;I grown and improved my&nbsp;skills using communication with my&nbsp;team members&nbsp;— real professionals in&nbsp;IT area. I’m very thankful to&nbsp;this company and recommend&nbsp;it!</p>
		</div>

